=cut

__DATA__

# --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=head1 NAME

cdecl - C gibberish into english

=head1 SYNOPSIS

 cdecl [options] [file]

=head1 NOTES

cdecl is an alias to cscan --get cdecl.

=head1 SEE ALSO

L<cscan>
